---
layout: base.njk
title: Solution Providers
---

<h1>Solution Providers</h1>

<p class="lead">Organizations providing expertise, services, and solutions to support community-driven transformation.</p>

<section>
    {% if solutionProviders.length > 0 %}
        {% for org in solutionProviders %}
        <article class="member-card">
            <h3>{{ org.name }}</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{ org.location }}{% if org.neighborhoods.length > 0 %}, {{ org.neighborhoods | join(", ") }}{% endif %}</p>
            <p><strong>Focus Areas:</strong> {{ org.domains | formatDomains }}</p>

            {% if org.offers.length > 0 %}
            <h4>What They Offer</h4>
            <ul>
                {% for offer in org.offers %}
                <li>{{ offer }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            {% endif %}

            {% if org.asks.length > 0 %}
            <h4>What They're Looking For</h4>
            <ul>
                {% for ask in org.asks %}
                <li>{{ ask }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            {% endif %}

            {% if org.website %}
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="{{ org.website }}" target="_blank">{{ org.website }}</a></p>
            {% endif %}

            {% if org.contact and org.contact.email %}
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ org.contact.email }}">{{ org.contact.email }}</a>{% if org.contact.person %} ({{ org.contact.person }}){% endif %}</p>
            {% endif %}

            <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{ org.status | capitalize }} member since {{ org.joined | formatDate }}</p>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
        <p>No solution providers listed yet. Check back soon!</p>
    {% endif %}
</section>

<section class="cta-box">
    <h2>Become a Solution Provider</h2>
    <p>Are you an organization providing expertise, services, or solutions for community transformation? Join our network of solution providers.</p>
    <p>We welcome:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Research institutions and think tanks</li>
        <li>NGOs and social enterprises</li>
        <li>Consultancies and service providers</li>
        <li>Technology and innovation labs</li>
        <li>Training and capacity building organizations</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:nudge-unit@notf.in">nudge-unit@notf.in</a> to join.</p>
</section>
